    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors are appropriately not assessed at MRL 2. Validation comparison demonstrates RHI prediction error within acceptance criterion across all 5 operating points. The analysis team notes that the primary benchmark validation result was generated under solver build ansys-cfx-2026-q1-build-7-rc2 rather than the released ansys-cfx-2026-q1-build-7; however, the team judges these builds to be effectively identical, as no solver patches were merged after the rc2 tag and the release differed only in internal QA labelling. On this basis the credibility package is accepted at Medium assurance level for MRL 2.",
